(1, 'Lorem dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed aliquam a libero non porttitor. Maecenas sit amet libero id est dignissim ornare. Integer sagittis, elit ut rhoncus lacinia, enim diam semper dolor.....', 'About Us', '<section class=\"cstm-about-section about_page_sec cstm-apprentice-sec\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<div class=\"inner_space\" data-aos=\"zoom-out-down\">\r\n<h2>APPRENTICESHIPS </h2>\r\n<p>In recent years, apprenticeships have become an incredibly popular career option for young people - and adults - alike. It is a way in which individuals are able to earn, while they learn, gaining valuable skills and knowledge in a specific job role. As we were founded by a freelance tutor, trainer and education practitioner, we completely understand the benefits that this method of training brings to both employers and the apprentices. The role helps the apprentice gain the knowledge, skills and behaviours they need to achieve the apprenticeship with support from the employer - hopefully providing them with a full-time role at the end of the duration.</p>\r\n<p>For companies, hiring apprentices is one of the most effective ways for a business to grow naturally - establishing a devoted, skilled and qualified team of individuals. Attracting quality talent can often be a real struggle, as younger generations are looking for an organisation which provides them with a purpose, which is why apprenticeships are such a great option. By hiring an apprentice, the company has the ability to ‘mould’ the individuals and their own culture, making changes to ensure it is better aligned with the wants and needs of the today’s workforce.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<div class=\"about_page_img\" data-aos=\"flip-left\" data-aos-easing=\"ease-out-cubic\" data-aos-duration=\"2000\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"height: 200px; width: auto;\" src=\"../public/web/images/APP_Logo_RGB_text_BLK.JPG\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class=\"cstm-apprentice\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n<p>Apprenticeships assure that employees have effective and up-to-date skills in order to enhance performance, productivity, competitiveness - whilst reducing employee turnover. By recruiting and equipping apprentices, these individuals can be developed individually to your company and develop the particular skills required by your business and industry. Apprenticeships are a clear signal that you are prepared to invest in the future; that you care about your staff and their level of qualification in your industry.</p>\r\n<p>Here at Freelance Genie, we can provide employers with freelance tutors and trainers for their apprentices. We are becoming the UK’s no.1 home for freelance tutors and trainers, from a wide range of different industries. Our apprentice trainers will deliver high quality, innovative teaching and learning to apprentices to help them progress throughout their programme.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class=\"cstm-about-section about_page_sec cstm-apprentice-sec\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<div class=\"about_page_img\" data-aos=\"flip-left\" data-aos-easing=\"ease-out-cubic\" data-aos-duration=\"2000\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"../public/web/images/about_3.png\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<div class=\"inner_space\" data-aos=\"zoom-out-down\">\r\n<h2>GOVERNMENT FUNDED COURSES</h2>\r\n<p>Many people are always looking to enhance their knowledge, which is why the government provide funded adult education courses across a range of sectors. These are often the ideal training solution for current employees, allowing staff to excel further in their current role with a nationally recognised qualification.</p>\r\n<p>Training and development within the workplace is very important for employees, which we especially understand as professionals who have spent over 20 years within education, learning & development and W2W sectors. Government-funded courses present a prime opportunity to expand the knowledge base of all employees, as development opportunities can be expensive. As the courses are completely funded, the employee who receives the necessary training is more equipped to perform in their job without a huge cost to the employer. These qualifications offer a great training resource to help improve and upskill your team. </p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class=\"cstm-apprentice\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n<p>From an employer’s point of view, staff are more likely to feel valued if they are invested in and therefore, less likely to change employers when government-funded courses are part of their day. Ongoing training and upskilling of the workforce can also encourage creativity, with increased efficiencies in processes resulting in financial gain for the corporation. Training also makes a company more attractive to potential new recruits who seek to improve their skills and the opportunities associated with those new skills. The better employees understand their position within the business, and how to achieve positive results, the more productively they can perform.</p>\r\n<p>With government-funded courses, this creates a whole team of knowledgeable staff with employees who can take over for one another as needed, without the need to have help and supervision - as they are able to work independently and thrive within a team. Training and development within an organisation is truly seen as a company benefit, showing staff that they feel valued and help your business adapt to change and prepare for growth.</p>\r\n<p>With Freelance Genie, you can find support from specialist trainers and tutors for almost any specialism including, NVQ\'s, QCF\'s, ESOL, Digital Marketing, Security, Childcare, Hospitality and more. We offer opportunities for government-funded courses to be carried out by freelance tutors, trainers and subcontractors online who have each been fully vetted and verified. </p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section id=\"about-main\" class=\"cstm-about-section about_page\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<div class=\"inner_space\" data-aos=\"zoom-out-up\">\r\n<h2>FREELANCE GENIE</h2>\r\n<p>Freelance genie was founded in 2015 and recently incorporated in 2019 by a Freelance Tutor, Trainer and Education Practitioner based in the West Midlands, who having spent 20 years in the Education and Training Industry, set out with &lsquo;1 mission&rsquo;,&hellip; To provide employers complete access to freelance tutors and trainers, by simplifying and modernising the process into a complete and unique &lsquo;online solution&rsquo;.</p>\r\n<p><em style=\"display: block; color: #e8058e;\">&ldquo;No more Small Talk, Only Big Action!&rdquo;</em> <em style=\"display: block; color: #e8058e;\">&ldquo;Convenience all in 1 place!&rdquo;</em> <em style=\"display: block; color: #e8058e;\">&ldquo;The ultimate resource for sourcing freelance Tutors and Trainers online&rdquo;</em></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<div class=\"about_page_img\" data-aos=\"flip-left\" data-aos-easing=\"ease-out-cubic\" data-aos-duration=\"2000\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"../public/web/images/about_page.png\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class=\"cstm-about-section about_page_sec\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<div class=\"about_page_img\" data-aos=\"flip-left\" data-aos-easing=\"ease-out-cubic\" data-aos-duration=\"2000\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"../public/web/images/about_2.png\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<div class=\"inner_space\" data-aos=\"zoom-out-down\">\r\n<h2>OUR AIMS ARE SIMPLE</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>To provide employers access to the best freelance tutor and trainer support, <span style=\"color: #e8058e;\">all online</span>.</li>\r\n<li>Becoming the UKs No.1 home for Freelance Tutors and Trainers that truly delivers on <span style=\"color: #e8058e;\">work life balance</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>We got rid of the antiquated, overburdening, time-consuming tasks and created a simple, effective, affordable solution covering all of your needs.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #e8058e;\">Join us inside</span> and see what we&rsquo;ve done.</p>\r\n<p><em style=\"display: block; color: #e8058e;\">&ldquo;From Personal to Virtual&rdquo;</em> <em style=\"display: block; color: #e8058e;\">&ldquo;We&rsquo;ve taken the personal touch, and added a Virtual Touch&rdquo;.</em></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class=\"cstm-about-section about_page\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<div class=\"inner_space\" data-aos=\"zoom-out-right\">\r\n<h2>Freelance Tutors &amp; Trainers</h2>\r\n<p>As Freelance Tutors and Trainers ourselves, we totally understand the Key challenges you face, not only in finding and securing work but also in maintaining work. We also understand the frustrations that come with being freelance, such as the course cancellations often at short notice, the course misallocations, and breakdowns in communication.</p>\r\n<p>Well, we have solved the problem! Enabling you to maintain a healthy work-life balance, with the ability to still maximise your earning potential. <span style=\"color: #e8058e;\">Join us inside</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<div class=\"about_page_img\" data-aos=\"flip-left\" data-aos-easing=\"ease-out-cubic\" data-aos-duration=\"2000\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"../public/web/images/about_3.png\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class=\"cstm-about-section about_page_sec\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<div class=\"about_page_img\" data-aos=\"flip-left\" data-aos-easing=\"ease-out-cubic\" data-aos-duration=\"2000\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"../public/web/images/about_4.png\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<div class=\"inner_space\" data-aos=\"zoom-out-left\">\r\n<h2>Note to Employers.</h2>\r\n<p>As Education Professionals who have spent over 20 years within Education, Learning &amp; Development and W2W sectors, working closely with senior managers, government officials and course designers, we also understand your needs. We provide you with both Internal &amp; External compliance towards your legal and regulatory requirements, which isn&rsquo;t just fundamental but crucial factors that impact on your reputation and success. Now you can gain access to the best possible freelance talent, quickly, easily and efficiently, all in one place, like never before&rsquo;. <span style=\"color: #e8058e;\">Join us inside</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class=\"cstm-about-section about_together\" data-aos=\"flip-up\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n<h2>LET&rsquo;S WORK TOGETHER!</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-7\">\r\n<p>Freelance genie, is a complete and unique platform, specifically designed to bridge the gap between Employers &amp; Freelance Tutors and Trainers in a totally modern and transparent way, all across the UK.</p>\r\n<p>By combining over 20 years of valuable knowledge and experience, we&rsquo;ve taken away all of the antiquated, over burdening, time consuming methods and created a simple but effective online solution to cover all of your needs.</p>\r\n<p>From Welfare 2 Work Tutors and Trainers, delivering ESOL or Employability course programs, QCF and NVQ Assessors, End-Point-Assessors, Internal &amp; External Verifiers, Moderators, CQC Mandatory short courses and MORE, we&rsquo;ve got you covered! <span style=\"color: #e8058e;\">Join us inside</span></p>\r\n<p>With Freelance genie, you can find Tutor &amp; Trainer support for almost any specialism, all online.</p>\r\n<p>Don&rsquo;t worry, you can still expect to maintain your quality, performance &amp; service or it may even improve your overall quality and performance, whilst saving you valuable time, resources and money to help you focus on what you do best!&ndash; You won&rsquo;t look back!</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-5\">\r\n<ul class=\"bullet_point\">\r\n<li>Freelance genie aims to become the number 1 resource tool for all industries that require Freelance Tutor/Trainer support by providing a one stop solution for all your Training/Tutor support needs:</li>\r\n<li><i class=\"fas fa-angle-right\"></i>24/7 Access</li>\r\n<li><i class=\"fas fa-angle-right\"></i>Easy to manage functionalities</li>\r\n<li><i class=\"fas fa-angle-right\"></i>Full Vetting/On boarding</li>\r\n<li><i class=\"fas fa-angle-right\"></i>Staff that start quicker</li>\r\n<li><i class=\"fas fa-angle-right\"></i>Reduced course cancellations, due to Holidays, Sickness or Absences</li>\r\n<li><i class=\"fas fa-angle-right\"></i>Robust control Measures</li>\r\n<li><i class=\"fas fa-angle-right\"></i>Full Transparency and Compliance</li>\r\n<li><i class=\"fas fa-angle-right\"></i>Reliability and Efficiency</li>\r\n<li><i class=\"fas fa-angle-right\"></i>Easy Sign up options</li>\r\n<li><i class=\"fas fa-angle-right\"></i>Flexible payment options</li>\r\n<li><i class=\"fas fa-angle-right\"></i>VALUE FOR MONEY</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\" style=\"margin-top: 40px;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12 text-center\">\r\n<p><strong><em>We built this for you! So OUR success is YOUR success!</em></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><em>NVQ\'s, QCF\'s, ESOL, Employability, Digital Marketing, I.T, Business, Security, Childcare, Hospitality, Customer Service ,Warehousing &amp; Logistics, Financial Services,Health &amp; Safety, Health &amp; Social, Personal Fitness, CQC Mandatory Training &amp; Independent Social Workers.</em></strong></p>\r\n<strong style=\"color: #e8058e;\"><em>We\'ve got you covered!</em></strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>', NULL, '2019-09-02 16:18:21'),
